attributes.description:
The Toyota Fortuner remains South Africa's top selling SUV, with ample interior space, as well as 7 seats, Toyota's undeniable reliability, 4x4 off-road prowess, and a phenomenal resale value. Powering the Fortuner is a 2.8L turbo diesel engine with 130Kw and a very respectable 420Nm of torque, which is mated to a 6 speed automatic gearbox driving all four wheels. This particular Fortuner has been conveniently equipped with a tow bar, nudge bar, roof rack, smash n grab safety film and durable high quality seat covers in the front.

Don't Miss Out, Call Us Today, or Leave Your Details and We Will Call You.

attributes.description:
HAVAL’s H1 compact crossover is a smash-hit sales success in global markets, and is also loved by South Africa’s trendy urbanites. Sporting fresh looks and lots of features as standard, the H1 represents (very) affordable crossover attitude. Its raised ground clearance makesit a confident runner in the urban jungle or on gravel roads, and the interior’s host of entertainment featuresmakes sure that the road trip never gets boring.
The H1 is powered by HAVAL’s trusty 1,5-litre VVT-i engine that delivers 69,3 kW at 6 000 rpm and 130 Nm of torque to the front wheels via a slick five-speed manual transmission.
Conveniently control all your entertainment from radio and CD to USB and Auxiliary formats, Bluetooth connectivity and the H1’s Cruise Control system from your steering wheel. Your hands will never need to leave the wheel again!
Nationwide delivery. All Trade-in's welcome. Finance can be arranged, Contact us today! Price excludes on the road fees.
